baseline_groups.claim_summary: Flooded counties experienced larger declines in Black population share (log) after the 1927 Mississippi flood, using county and state-year FE with continuous flood intensity treatment.
baseline_groups.notes: Baseline uses lnfrac_black outcome, flood_intensity treatment, County FE + State-Year FE, clustered at fips. baseline_lagged_dv has null treatment coef. Baseline coef is 0.026, p=0.63.

global_notes: Issues: (1) baseline coef small and insignificant. (2) 8 specs have null treatment coefs. (3) Cross-section specs estimate different model. (4) Some FE specs omit critical identification. (5) frac_black outcome and levels funcform are duplicates.
